[Gould blubbers]

751
00:37:16,901 --> 00:37:18,569
[man]
Give us a dance!

752
00:37:18,603 --> 00:37:20,938
I'll give you
a dance I learned...

753
00:37:20,972 --> 00:37:24,208
on a South Dakota reservation
from the Chippewa Indians.

754
00:37:24,242 --> 00:37:27,812
It's called the Joseph
Ferdinand Gould stomp!

755
00:37:27,845 --> 00:37:29,413
Listen to this!

756
