1995
01:41:36,223 --> 01:41:37,991
Might be able
to write out here.

1996
01:41:44,198 --> 01:41:45,933
I'm glad I was able
to see you, Joe.

1997
01:41:49,369 --> 01:41:50,871
When you see
all those folks...

1998
01:41:52,473 --> 01:41:53,407
tell them...

1999
01:41:56,276 --> 01:41:57,277
it wasn't...

2000
01:42:04,284 --> 01:42:06,620
It was never
a question of laziness.

2001
01:42:14,428 --> 01:42:15,562
Bye, Joe.

2002
01:42:50,164 --> 01:42:53,534
